Special: **THE DAWN OF THE FIRST DAY**, our heroes find themselves at a crossroeads. Each needing to leave their homes to travel deep into a haunted wood, but none willing to do it alone, but with the king's soldiers at their back with swords drawn, chasing them away from the only homes they've ever known, they don't have much of a choice. It's either stay behind and be slain by the kings men, or take their chances in the haunted wood.
